  "text": "1-10 3 \u03eb 10 5 LC-enriched ECs per well were seeded as stimulator cells. Responders and stimulators were cocultured in 96-well round-bottomed plates at 37 \u040a C in 200 l of complete medium. All cultures were pulsed overnight with 0.2 Ci [ 3 H]TdR, and incorporated radioactivity was assessed by liquid scintillation counting [CITATION_1] .",
